<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>A <rs type="material">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">altar-stele</rs> with moulding above and below on three sides (<measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.81</measure> x <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.43</measure> x <measure dim="depth" type="length" unit="metre">0.355</measure>). The relief, very worn, is of a <rs type="decoration">bestiarius</rs> facing towards his left, from where a beast - - ?a <rs type="decoration">bear</rs> - - is springing up at him</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the face</p>
</div>
